textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+ \S+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value LOCAL_LABEL (\d+)
Value REMOTE_LABEL (\d+)
Value GROUP_ID (\S+)
Value VC_ID (\d+)
Value VC_STATUS (\S+)
Value PREFERRED_PATH (\S+ \S+)
Value DEFAULT_PATH (\S+)
Value NEXT_HOP (\S+)

Start
  ^Local interface: ${INTERFACE} [\s\S]+ ${STATE}$$
  ^\s*MPLS VC labels: local ${LOCAL_LABEL}, remote ${REMOTE_LABEL}$$
  ^\s*Group ID: ${GROUP_ID},$$
  ^\s*VC ID: ${VC_ID},$$
  ^\s*VC status: ${VC_STATUS}, Preferred path: ${PREFERRED_PATH}$$
  ^\s*Default path: ${DEFAULT_PATH}, Next hop: ${NEXT_HOP}$$ -> Record
